## Changes

### 游냍 Fixed
- SpriteRenderer - Fix eslint max-len usage #3544
- Ensure that polyfills are imported first #3543
- Locally cache `this.texture` #3531
- Fix compute Text canvas size. #3519 
- Rebind `vao` before `glData` upload. #3455
- Fix `cacheAsBitmap` for CanvasRender for nested elements. #3494
- Bug with TilingSprite anchor behavior #3536 
- Problem with render when `cacheAsBitmap` and mask are used together #3545 
- Fixes check in Sprite for `calculateVertices` #3554
- Updated documentation #3529 #3548 #3553 #3555 #3597 #3591 #3603 #3604

### 游꾸 Added
- Added overlapping children tests #3535 
- Add constructor param in AnimatedSprite to disable `PIXI.ticker.shared` self-updates #3429
- Adds `PIXI.Application` class for creating renderer #3551 #3601

``` js
// OLD: implementation requires setting up a renderer, 
// Container for the stage and the update loop
const renderer = PIXI.autoDetectRenderer(800, 600);
document.body.appendChild(renderer.view);
const stage = new PIXI.Container();
const sprite = PIXI.Sprite.fromImage("foo.png");
stage.addChild(sprite);
function update() {
    sprite.rotation += 0.01;
    renderer.render(stage);
    requestAnimationFrame(update);
}
update();

// NEW: Introduces Application which handles the 
// setup of the stage, renderer and ticker AND
// the Application class can be inherited!
const app = new PIXI.Application(800, 600);
document.body.appendChild(app.view);
const sprite = PIXI.Sprite.fromImage("foo.png");
app.stage.addChild(sprite);
app.ticker.add(() => {
   sprite.rotation += 0.01;
});
```

### 游눯 Changed
- Use high precision float instead of medium in texture shader #3353
- Remove needless `Number()` call #3552
- Rectangle test updates #3578 
- Preserve mocha scope #3599

Commits: https://github.com/pixijs/pixi.js/compare/v4.3.2...v4.3.3
